'''Jacayl''' ama '''[[Jecayl]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: love; af-[[carabi]]: ﻋﺸﻖ ama ﺍﻟﺤﺐ; Giriik: ἀγάπη; Eros: ἔρως; af-[[Shiinaha|Shiine]]: 愛; Beershiyaan: eshgh "ishqi"; Filiya: φιλία; Roman: amō; af-Budhe: 愛; af[[Jabaan]]: 甘え "amae"; af-[[Turki]]: Aşık; Hebrew: Ahava) waa dareen, marxalad, hami, doonid, xaalad iyo rabitaan [[qof]] u qaado ama hayo shey kale.<ref>'''[[Jecayl]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: love</ref> Sidoo kale, [[Jecayl]]ku waa qadarin, sharfid, xushmayn iyo ixtiraam qoto dheer oo qof u hayo noole, shey, qof ama arin kale. Tusaale ahaan, jacaylka [[hooyo]] iyo [[aabo]]; jacaylka [[Alle]]; kan qof kale ([[lab]] ama [[dhidig]]); jaceylka shey ama walax sida [[baabuur]], [[buug]], [[filim]], [[hees]] iwm.<ref>"af-[[carabi]]: ﻋﺸﻖ ama ﺍﻟﺤﺐ"</ref><ref>"Giriik: ἀγάπη; Eros: ἔρως; af-[[Shiinaha|Shiine]]: 愛; Beershiyaan: eshgh "ishqi"; Filiya: φιλία; Roman: amō;"</ref><ref>"Filiya: φιλία; Roman: amō; af-Budhe: 愛; af[[Jabaan]]: 甘え "amae"; af-[[Turki]]: Aşık; Hebrew: Ahava"</ref> 

Guud ahaan, Jacaylku waa dareen [[qof]] u hayo wax kale noocuu doonaba ha ahaadee.<ref>"Jacaylku waa dareen [[qof]] u hayo wax kale noocuu doonaba ha ahaadee"</ref> Intaas waxaa dheer, jecaylku wuu noocyo iyo qaabab badan yahay, waxaana jira ugu yaraan [[toban]] nooc oo jacayl ah. Kuwaas waxaa ka mid ah:
:*[[Diin|Jacaylka diinta]]
:*[[Waalid|Jacaylka waalidka]]
:*[[Walaal|Jacaylka walaalaha]]
:*[[Ubad|Jacaylka ubadka]] (caruurta ama ciyaalka)
:*[[qof|Jacaylka qof]] sida [[gabadh]] ama [[wiil]]
